[background arg="#000000ff" fade="0.0"]
do SceneManager.change_scene("res://TAK TAK TAK.tscn")
join Steve (Default) left
Steve: Did you find it?
if {Hat2} == true:
	label Hat found!
	- Yes
		Steve: You shouldn't have bothered.
		- I thought you wanted your hat.
		Steve: I do...
		Steve: I want people to look at the Hat and not me.
		- Does it help?
		join Steve (hat) left
		Steve: Enough...
		Steve: .....
		- Is it time to go yet?
		Steve: Ya...
		Steve: Before I lose it again...
		Steve: This Hat does look really good on me eh?
		- It does.
		Steve: Hold on tight!
		jump 1
		[end_timeline]
elif {Hat2} == false:
	- no
	Steve: You search the area while I search the soul.
	do SceneManager.change_scene("res://Scenes/Maps/Bridge_2.tscn")
	[end_timeline]
label 1
do SceneManager.change_scene("res://Scenes/Maps/final_area.tscn")